=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 30, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xio1665702655482.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xio1665702655482.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xio1665702655482.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xio1665702655482\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xio1665702655482__topic_d141164e1_d141165e1_d141166e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xio1665702655482__p_d141167e1_d141168e1_d141169e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LISTING_LEVEL</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xio1665702655482__section_mjs_rx4_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212054e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Script Listing Level</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__2\">Generates a basic script listing with no\n                     precompiler directives.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16832e1_d16833e1_d16834e1__entry__2\">Generates a script listing that includes\n\t\t\t\t precompiler directives</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xio1665702655482__section_fzz_sx4_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212054e124\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xio1665702655482__table_d16835e1_d16836e1_d16837e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.asn</span>,\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> [SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">none</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xio1665702655482__section_tj4_vx4_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1212054e174\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xio1665702655482__p_d141191e1_d141192e1_d141193e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LISTING_LEVEL</span> setting to\n        produce compile listings of components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript\n        modules.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xio1665702655482__p_d141194e1_d141195e1_d141196e1\">If the message level is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">info</code>\n        (using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span> sub-switch), the listing includes additional compilation\n        messages, including errors, warnings and info messages.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xio1665702655482__p_d141197e1_d141198e1_d141199e1\">If this setting is not defined, no listing is\n        generated.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xio1665702655482__p_d141200e1_d141201e1_d141202e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LISTING_LEVEL</span> setting is\n        ignored when the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lis</span> command line sub-switch is used.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfm1665702655413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Script Listings</a><p>A script listing is an ASCII file containing a concatenated list of all the compiled script in a component, application shell, menu, or global ProcScript. Separate script listings are generated for script in entity collection and entity occurrence triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybj1665702655557.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Generate and View Script Listings</a><p>You can configure Uniface to generate script listings by setting the $LISTING_LEVEL assignment setting or by using the /lis command line switch.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/stn1665702655266.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/lis</a><p>Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules for components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/czj1665702653450.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/inf</a><p>Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$LISTING_LEVEL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 30, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules. $LISTING_LEVEL { = } 1 | 2 Arguments Table 1. Script Listing Level Value Meaning 1 Generates a basic script listing with no precompiler directives. 2 Generates a script listing that includes precompiler directives Defaults Assignment file: usys.asn , ide.asn Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: none Description Use the $LISTING_LEVEL setting to produce compile listings of components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript modules. If the message level is set to info (using /inf sub-switch), the listing includes additional compilation messages, including errors, warnings and info messages. If this setting is not defined, no listing is generated. The $LISTING_LEVEL setting is ignored when the /lis command line sub-switch is used. Related Links Script Listings A script listing is an ASCII file containing a concatenated list of all the compiled script in a component, application shell, menu, or global ProcScript. Separate script listings are generated for script in entity collection and entity occurrence triggers. Generate and View Script Listings You can configure Uniface to generate script listings by setting the $LISTING_LEVEL assignment setting or by using the /lis command line switch. /lis Produce compile listings of ProcScript modules for components, application shells, menus, and global ProcScript. /inf Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}